reviewText: While those from other parts of the country would probably rate this as the usual fare for railroad video, for me it's loaded with memories along a route I've travelled many times on the adjacent Highway 61. It opens with a shot from John Latsch State Park where they (and I) had to climb hundreds of stair steps to reach that lofty spot. I won't soon forget that climb and thanks to this video, I'll always have a reminder of that day.
